name: Antivid - Covid19 Anticipation Super App
description: This is Antivid, a Covid-19 anticipation super app. Available features include: Distance alert, radar view, alert friends, e-wallet, e-payment, social media, Covid-19 news, PeduliLindungi, vaccine, PCR, find doctor, find quarantine places, telemedicine, explore healthy foods, Covid-19 tracing, and readings about Covid-19 regulations. Tools that I use is: Figma, Flaticon, Unsplash, and Dribbble. I made this for about four weeks. You can criticize my design at the comment section. Thank you!
